Hey, don't you hurt my dog!

1152
01:38:54,888 --> 01:38:59,226
- Don't you make me hurt your dog!
- Oh, you don't know what pain is!

1153
01:39:04,523 --> 01:39:08,318
Get me a live telephone line down here
or the dog's dead!

1154
01:39:12,698 --> 01:39:13,657
Damn fuck.

1155
01:39:13,824 --> 01:39:15,701
Get me that telephone!

1156
01:39:17,244 --> 01:39:19,204
I'm gonna do it, mister!

1157
01:39:19,455 --> 01:39:22,791
I'll snap her neck off. I swear to God!

1158
01:39:23,917 --> 01:39:25,502
You little fuck.

1159
01:39:32,509 --> 01:39:35,053
Down here! Down here!

1160
01:39:35,220 --> 01:39:36,472
Help!

1161
01:39:49,151 --> 01:39:51,028
Okay, I'm coming.

1162
01:39:53,155 --> 01:39:54,656
We're going in.

1163
01:39:59,328 --> 01:40:01,914
Good afternoon. Sorry to bother you.

1164
01:40:02,331 --> 01:40:04,082
I'm looking for Mrs. Lippman's family.

1165
01:40:04,750 --> 01:40:07,503
- FBI! Everybody down!
- Everybody down, now!

1166
01:40:07,836 --> 01:40:09,476
No. The Lippmans don't live here anymore.

1167
01:40:09,588 --> 01:40:12,633
No. Excuse me, sir.
I really need to speak with you.

1168
01:40:13,592 --> 01:40:15,344
- Clear!
- Clear!

1169
01:40:16,136 --> 01:40:18,347
What's the problem, Officer?

1170
01:40:18,514 --> 01:40:21,934
Well, I'm investigating the death
of Fredrica Bimmel.

1171
01:40:24,686 --> 01:40:26,188
There's no one here, Jack.

1172
01:40:28,649 --> 01:40:29,900
Clarice.

1173
01:40:30,192 --> 01:40:31,318
Your name is?

1174
01:40:31,485 --> 01:40:34,029
- Oh, Jack Gordon.
- Mr. Gordon. Good.

1175
01:40:34,988 --> 01:40:38,408
Well, Fredrica used to work
for Mrs. Lippman. Did you know her?

1176
01:40:39,117 --> 01:40:40,452
No.

1177
01:40:41,411 --> 01:40:42,704
Oh, wait.

1178
01:40:43,080 --> 01:40:45,374
Was she a great, big fat person?

1179
01:40:46,208 --> 01:40:48,919
- Yes. She was a big girl, sir.
- Yeah, I...

1180
01:40:49,253 --> 01:40:52,089
I may have...
No, I read about her in the newspaper.

1181
01:40:54,091 --> 01:40:56,510
Mrs. Lippman had a son.
Maybe he could help you.

1182
01:40:56,677 --> 01:40:59,972
I got his card in here someplace. Do
you want to come in while I look for it?

1183
01:41:00,138 --> 01:41:01,223
- May I?
- Yeah, sure.

1184
01:41:01,390 --> 01:41:02,683
Thank you.

1185
01:41:21,410 --> 01:41:23,912
Are you close to catching somebody,
you think?

1186
01:41:25,038 --> 01:41:26,999
Yes. We may be.

1187
01:41:29,418 --> 01:41:30,669
Did you

1188
01:41:31,587 --> 01:41:34,756
take over this place
after Mrs. Lippman died? Is that right?

1189
01:41:36,508 --> 01:41:40,554
Yeah. I bought this house two years ago.

1190
01:41:42,097 --> 01:41:45,225
Did she leave any records,
any business records,

1191
01:41:45,642 --> 01:41:48,770
tax forms, list of employees?

1192
01:41:49,980 --> 01:41:52,190
No. Nothing like that at all.

1193
01:41:54,443 --> 01:41:56,945
Say, has the FBI learned something?

1194
01:41:57,362 --> 01:42:00,240
The police around here
don't seem to have the first clue.

1195
01:42:10,250 --> 01:42:14,880
I mean, have you got, like, a description,
fingerprints, anything like that?

1196
01:42:16,298 --> 01:42:17,341
No.

1197
01:42:20,260 --> 01:42:21,720
No, we don't.

1198
01:42:31,146 --> 01:42:33,774
Yeah. Here's that number.

1199
01:42:35,817 --> 01:42:39,154
Very good, Mr. Gordon.
May I use your phone, please?

1200
01:42:47,746 --> 01:42:49,790
Sure you can use my phone.

1201
01:42:51,166 --> 01:42:52,376
Freeze!

1202
01:42:53,168 --> 01:42:56,713
Put your hands over your head!
And turn around! Spread your legs!

1203
01:42:58,340 --> 01:43:01,802
Spread your legs!
Put your hands in the back! Thumbs up!

1204
01:43:01,968 --> 01:43:02,928
Freeze!

1205
01:44:15,917 --> 01:44:17,419
Hey!

1206
01:44:37,606 --> 01:44:39,566
Hello! Are you there?

1207
01:44:41,485 --> 01:44:43,820
I'm down here! I'm down here!

1208
01:45:03,965 --> 01:45:06,676
- Catherine Martin?
- Yes!

1209
01:45:08,804 --> 01:45:11,264
FBI! You're safe!

1210
01:45:11,807 --> 01:45:14,226
Safe, shit! Get me out of here!

1211
01:45:29,866 --> 01:45:31,910
You're all right, Catherine. Where is he?

1212
01:45:32,077 --> 01:45:34,996
How the fuck should I know?
Just get me out of here!

1213
01:45:35,163 --> 01:45:38,208
Catherine, you've got to be quiet.
Now shut that dog up!

1214
01:45:38,375 --> 01:45:40,418
Just get me out of here!

1215
01:45:41,503 --> 01:45:42,921
Oh, my God.

1216
01:45:45,340 --> 01:45:47,551
Catherine, I'm going to get you
out of there,

1217
01:45:47,717 --> 01:45:49,386
but right now, you listen to me.

1218
01:45:49,553 --> 01:45:51,972
I've got to leave this room.
I'll be right back.

1219
01:45:52,138 --> 01:45:54,808
No! Don't you leave me here,
you fucking bitch!

1220
01:45:54,975 --> 01:45:57,394
No! Don't you leave me here!

1221
01:45:57,602 --> 01:45:59,855
This guy's fucking crazy!

1222
01:46:02,774 --> 01:46:04,359
Please!

1223
01:46:04,526 --> 01:46:07,821
I've got to get out of here!

1224
01:46:10,282 --> 01:46:14,202
Catherine, the other officers will be here
any minute now!

1225
01:46:15,203 --> 01:46:16,496
Wait!

1226
01:46:17,080 --> 01:46:18,915
Don't go! Please!

1227
01:46:19,082 --> 01:46:20,208
Quiet!

1228
01:46:22,752 --> 01:46:24,212
Oh, God!

1229
01:50:11,147 --> 01:50:12,148
No...

1230
01:50:21,241 --> 01:50:23,576
- You okay?
- Gunpowder. It's nothing. I'm okay.

1231
01:50:23,743 --> 01:50:26,788
Agent Starling, how did you track
Buffalo Bill to this address?

1232
01:50:33,044 --> 01:50:35,505
Clarice M. Starling.

1233
01:50:38,007 --> 01:50:39,634
Congratulations.

1234
01:50:52,897 --> 01:50:55,066
Ernest W. Stevens.

1235
01:51:13,668 --> 01:51:16,838
- Special Agent Starling.
- Oh, Special Agent Mapp.

1236
01:51:17,088 --> 01:51:18,464
- Phone call.
- Thank you.

1237
01:51:18,631 --> 01:51:20,925
- Excuse me, gentlemen.
- Starling.

1238
01:51:23,678 --> 01:51:26,139
Pilch, could you take our picture?

1239
01:51:26,681 --> 01:51:27,765
Sure.

1240
01:51:29,267 --> 01:51:32,103
Look,
I just wanted to say congratulations.

1241
01:51:32,478 --> 01:51:34,314
And I'm not much good
at this kind of thing,

1242
01:51:34,480 --> 01:51:36,191
so I'm gonna duck out of here.

1243
01:51:36,357 --> 01:51:37,567
Okay, sure.

1244
01:51:39,319 --> 01:51:41,196
Thank you, Mr. Crawford.

1245
01:51:48,870 --> 01:51:51,581
Your father would have been proud today.

1246
01:51:54,542 --> 01:51:56,711
Don't forget your phone call.

1247
01:52:00,965 --> 01:52:02,300
Starling.

1248
01:52:02,467 --> 01:52:06,763
Well, Clarice,
have the lambs stopped screaming?

1249
01:52:07,472 --> 01:52:08,640
Dr. Lecter.

1250
01:52:08,890 --> 01:52:11,809
Don't bother with a trace.
I won't be on long enough.

1251
01:52:15,438 --> 01:52:19,609
- Where are you, Dr. Lecter?
- I have no plans to call on you, Clarice.

1252
01:52:19,776 --> 01:52:22,237
The world's more interesting
with you in it.

1253
01:52:22,779 --> 01:52:25,907
<i>So you take care now
to extend me the same courtesy.</i>

1254
01:52:26,074 --> 01:52:28,451
You know I can't make that promise.

1255
01:52:29,035 --> 01:52:31,704
I do wish we could chat longer, but...

1256
01:52:32,747 --> 01:52:35,291
I'm having an old friend for dinner.

1257
01:52:36,876 --> 01:52:37,919
Bye.

1258
01:52:38,586 --> 01:52:40,004
<i>Dr. Lecter...</i>

1259
01:52:42,423 --> 01:52:43,800
Dr. Lecter.

1260
01:52:46,094 --> 01:52:47,470
Dr. Lecter.

1261
01:52:49,472 --> 01:52:50,848
Dr. Lecter.

1262
01:52:51,391 --> 01:52:53,518
Hey, what? Oh, excuse me. I'm sorry.

1263
01:52:53,810 --> 01:52:56,729
- Is the security system all set up?
- We have the big-shot security.

1264
01:52:56,896 --> 01:52:58,356
Thank you. I appreciate that.

